<h4>View User</h4>
<h5>Key Features</h5>
<ul>
		<li>User Details</li>
		<li>Friendship Controls</li>
		<li>User Routes</li>
		<li>User Training Items</li>
</ul>

<h5>User Details</h5>
<p>The user details column contains information about regarding the user's
join date and the last date they accessed runnDAILY.</p>
<h5>Friendship Control</h5>
<p class="icon">If you would like to befriend a user in order to see their
route list and training items, select <img src="/img/icon/user_plus.png" /> <span
		class="bold"
>Add as Friend</span> to send a friend request to the user. If you are already
friends with a user and you wish to defriend them, select <img
		src="/img/icon/user_minus.png"
/> <span class="bold">Remove Friend</span>.</p>
<h5>User Routes</h5>
<p>A list of the current user's routes can be seen in the Routes column.This
list can be sorted using the drop down selector located directly above the list.
To reverse the sort order, select either <img src="/img/icon/sort_asc.png" /> <span
		class="bold"
>ASC</span> or <img src="/img/icon/sort_desc.png" /> <span class="bold">DESC</span>.</p>
<h5>User Training Items</h5>
<p>A list of the current user's training items can be seen in the Training
Items column.This list can be sorted using the drop down selector located
directly above the list. To reverse the sort order, select either <img
		src="/img/icon/sort_asc.png"
/> <span class="bold">ASC</span> or <img src="/img/icon/sort_desc.png" /> <span
		class="bold"
>DESC</span>.</p>